  * Support for AMD XDNA NPU (amd/xdna-driver)
  * Update libdrm_amdgpu_sys
    * Support for GFX12 family (RDNA 4), CHIP_GFX1200 and CHIP_GFX1201
    * Support for CHIP_GFX1103_R1X (Hawk Point1) and CHIP_GFX1103_R2X (Hawk Point2)
